      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just \"feeling\" like a weight. i see it. i see them struggling because of the stress i bring, the money i dont have, the way i just shut down. if i wasn't here, the house would be quieter, they wouldn't have to worry about my moods or my failures. it's like... if i just removed myself from the equation, they could finally breathe. it almost feels like the only selfless thing left to do is to stop being a burden.",
